    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Healthcare in Brazil</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Brazil has universal public healthcare (SUS) and excellent private options. Private healthcare in major cities is world-class; rural areas have limited access.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Private Hospitals</h3>

