      <li><strong>Hospital Sírio-Libanês (São Paulo):</strong> Top-tier private hospital</li>
      <li><strong>Copa Star (Rio):</strong> Modern private hospital in Copacabana</li>
      <li><strong>Hospital Moinhos de Vento (Porto Alegre):</strong> Excellent regional hospital</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Medical Tourism</h3>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Brazil is a medical tourism destination, especially for cosmetic surgery. High-quality care at lower costs than North America or Europe attracts international patients.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Sample Costs (Without Insurance)</h3>

