    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      The trade-offs are real: safety requires awareness, Portuguese is essential, and bureaucracy can be frustrating. But for nomads willing to embrace these challenges, Brazil rewards with warmth, beauty, and experiences found nowhere else.
    </p>

